He is also not unjust to forget all of America’s labor of love and missionary work that has been done throughout the years. There are also many good reports about America, and these things are not unseen by the Lord. Out of His great love for America, He has given us an opportunity to repent. He has given us an answer to stir and lead us to repentance. His answer for America is the move of Face to Face! Face to Face is the Answer to Turn Back America to God!

David E. Taylor loves America and sought God for an answer to turn the nation back to Him. These dreams (about the nuclear war from Russia) set him on a course to find the answer for America! Even though there are issues America needs to repent of, the Lord also sees the godly qualities of this nation, and He wants America to be saved. In his pursuit, the answer that he found from the Lord that can turn America back to Him is Face to Face! America is not listening to preachers, but they will listen to a face to face visitation from Jesus and the Father! This will get America’s attention! There is hope! There is an answer! And God is not finished with America! The move of face to face can save America and avert coming judgments! The move of face to face can save America and avert coming judgments!"

https://youtu.be/yglCr-sVz0o
